ick) |Score=ND 28-0}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=2 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Wolski 1-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score=ND 35-0}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=2 |Time= |Team=Pitt |Event=Dyer 21-yard pass from Lucas (kick blocked) |Score=ND 35-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=3 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Wolski 1-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score= ND 42-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=3 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Gmitter 44-yard pass from Zloch (kick blocked)|Score=ND 48-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=3 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=May 5-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score=ND 55-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Bleier 3-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score= ND 62-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Conway 2-yard run (Ivan kick)|Score=ND 69-6}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team=Pitt |Event=Zalansky 5-yard pass from James (Jones kick) |Score=ND 69-13|LastEntry=yes}}\n{{AFB game box end}}\n{{-}}\n{{Clear}}\n\n===North Carolina===\n{{AFB game box start\n|Title=\n|Visitor=N. Carolina\n|V1=0 |V2=0 |V3=0 |V4= 0\n|Host='''Notre Dame'''\n|H1=0 |H2=0 |H3=0 |H4=17\n|Date=November 13\n|Location=Notre Dame Stadium, South Bend, IN\n|StartTime=1:30 p.m.\n|TimeZone=Eastern\n|ElapsedTime=\n|Attendance=\n|Weather=\n|Referee=\n|TVAnnouncers=\n|TVStation=\n}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |FirstEntry=yes |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team= ND|Event=Ivan 38-yard field goal |Score= ND 3-0}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Eddy 66-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score= ND 10-0}}\n    {{AFB Game Box Scoring Entry |Quarter=4 |Time= |Team=ND |Event=Eddy 3-yard run (Ivan kick) |Score=ND 17-0 |LastEntry=yes}}\n{{AFB game box end}}\n{{-}}\n{{Clear}}\n\n===Michigan State===\n{{AFB game box start\n|Title=\n|Visitor='''Michigan St.'''\n|V1=0 |V2=0 |V3=6 |V4=6\n|Host='''Notre Dame'''\n|H1=3 |H2=0 |H3=0 |H4=0\n|Date=November 20\n|Location=Notre Dame Stadiu