e been infected; at least 91 have died.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/17/us-coronavirus-cases-surpass-5000-up-fivefold-from-a-week-ago.html |title=US coronavirus cases surpass 5,000, up fivefold from a week ago |last=Feuer |first=William |date=17 March 2020 |website=cnbc.com |access-date=March 18, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318041705/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/03/17/us-coronavirus-cases-surpass-5000-up-fivefold-from-a-week-ago.html |archive-date=March 18, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref> The [[Peace Corps]] fires all 7,300 volunteers in 61 countries.<ref>[https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/the-peace-corps-isnt-just-bringing-home-7300-volunteers-because-of-the-coronavirus-its-firing-them/2020/03/20/69aa08f4-6ac0-11ea-b5f1-a5a804158597_story.html?fbclid=IwAR2V2O_UEkvaRLs1bUEK9ydswZ-AqMbB-qPUtREkeUI0FyjEfu5qqbPcYlg The Peace Corps isn't just bringing home 7,300 volunteers because of the coronavirus. It's firing them.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320225745/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/the-peace-corps-isnt-just-bringing-home-7300-volunteers-because-of-the-coronavirus-its-firing-them/2020/03/20/69aa08f4-6ac0-11ea-b5f1-a5a804158597_story.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2V2O_UEkvaRLs1bUEK9ydswZ-AqMbB-qPUtREkeUI0FyjEfu5qqbPcYlg |date=March 20, 2020 }} by Joe Davidson, The Washington Post, 20 Mar 2020</ref>\n\n* Alabama: Alabama had a total of 39 cases, where the majority of them (21 cases) are located in Jefferson County.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fox10tv.com/news/coronavirus/alabama-now-up-to-confirmed-covid--cases/article_b0358ace-688f-11ea-8f19-0b5121c61b5b.html|title=Alabama now up to 39 confirmed COVID-19 cases|website=FOX10 News|language=en|access-date=2020-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318070159/https://www.fox10tv.com/news/coronavirus/alabama-now-up-to-confirmed-covid--cases/article_b0358ace-688f-11ea-8f19-0b5121c61b5b.html|archive-date=March 18, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n